.. _changelog:

================
 Change history
================

.. _version-1.3.0:

1.3.0
=====
:release-date: 2016-10-19 12:36:00 P.M PDT

- Adds cyanide.suite.ManagerMixin

.. _version-1.2.0:

1.2.0
=====
:release-date: 2016-06-30 11:27:00 P.M PDT

- ``celery vagrant``: Updates to new RabbitMQ APT key URL.

- New tasks: ``errback`` and ``old_errback`` for testing new canvas error
  callbacks.

- Integrates tests from old Celery functional test suite.

.. _version-1.1.0:

1.1.0
=====
:release-date: 2016-05-12 03:07:00 P.M PDT
:release-by: Ask Solem

- Moved tasks from ``cyanide.app`` into :mod:`cyanide.tasks`.

- Adds Suite.wait_for with progress bar.

- More useful harness output.

.. _version-1.0.1

1.0.1
=====
:release-date: 2106-04-26 06:42:00 P.M PDT
:release-by: Ask Solem

- Now compatible with Celery 3.1

.. _version-1.0.0

1.0.0
=====
:release-date: 2106-04-26 06:17:00 P.M PST
:release-by: Ask Solem

- Initial release assembled from ``celery/funtests/stress/``
